snippet.title: Starship Defense (DSiWare Gameplay)
snippet.description:
Starship Defense is a defense game where you have to shoot down the incoming enemies before they shoot you down. Accumulate energy and deploy all kinds of weapons to survive.

#Nintendo #DSi #DSiWare
